#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:1
msgid "E0014"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `alert` or `alert_<category>`"
msgstr "警告名称：`alert` 或 `alert_<category>`"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:5
msgid ""
"Alert warnings are emitted when code uses an API that the provider marked"
" with an alert attribute, such as [`#internal`](../attributes.md"
"#internal-attribute). The alert category is chosen by the API provider, "
"so the warning name can be `alert` for all alerts or `alert_<category>` "
"for one category."
msgstr ""
"当代码使用了 API 提供者通过 alert 属性（例如 "
"[`#internal`](../attributes.md#internal-attribute)）标记的 API 时，会发出 "
"alert 警告。Alert 的类别由 API 提供者选择，因此警告名称可以是用于所有 alert "
"的 `alert`，也可以是用于某一类别的 `alert_<category>`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:12
msgid ""
"The provider module marks `experimental` as internal, and the importing "
"module calls it:"
msgstr ""
"provider 模块将 `experimental` 标记为 internal，导入它的模块随后调用了"
"它："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:15
#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:30
msgid "provider/top.mbt"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:15
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"#internal(experimental, \"use stable instead\")\n"
"pub fn experimental() -> Int {\n"
"  1\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:20
#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:35
msgid "top.mbt"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:20
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(@provider.experimental(), content=\"1\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:25
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "修改建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:27
msgid ""
"Use a stable public API instead, or configure the specific alert category"
" only when the dependency intentionally exposes that API for your use "
"case."
msgstr ""
"请改用稳定的公开 API；只有当依赖项有意为你的使用场景暴露该 API 时，才配置对应"
"的 alert 类别。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:30
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn stable() -> Int {\n"
"  1\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:35
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(@provider.stable(), content=\"1\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

